d": true}, "short_span_min_tokens": {"details": {"min_tokens": 2, "token_count": 89}, "passed": true}}, "text": "1. SYRIA REPORTEDLY OFFERED MIG-17's\n\nComment\nThis is the first firm evidence that the Soviet bloc intends to sell MIG-17's to the Arab states.\n\nThe price quoted is about $8,000 higher than that asked for MIG-15's, and appears to be reasonable for this type of aircraft. MIG-17's have been previously rumored as included in the Egyptian arms deal but none is known to have been delivered. Syria now has 20 MIG-15's on order. The MIG-17 is superior to the French Mystere IV-A, the best aircraft the Israelis have", "token_count": 89, "token_end_0based": 88, "token_start_0based": 0, "token_text": "1 syria reportedly offered mig-17's comment this is the first firm evidence that the soviet bloc intends to sell mig-17's to the arab states the price quoted is about 8 000 higher than that asked for mig-15's and appears to be reasonable for this type of aircraft mig-17's have been previously rumored as included in the egyptian arms deal but none is known to have been delivered syria now has 20 mig-15's on order the mig-17 is superior to the french mystere iv-a the best aircraft the israelis have", "unred_source_page": 4}
